name: Shivam Family Restaurant

reviews.review_text: The crispy chicken and cheese garlic nan was a good combo. The staff behaviour is really good. The pricing is descent while comparing to other restaurants in Goa.

Though this restaurant is not that well known as other restaurants, this is one of the finest sea food restaurant in Goa.

The fish thali is outstanding. The service is impeccable. Ambience is good, not great though. But the food leaves a tangible taste in the tongue.

Will definitely visit many more times.

Highly recommended Fish Thali in Goa

The place is beautiful and on road so no confusion in finding the restaurant. The staff is very friendly and cooperative. Ordering is also easy. The fish thali contains a lot of dishes, affordable and all the dishes were tasty.
Overall it is a very great place to visit with your family.

description:
### Shiva Family Restaurant: A Hidden Gem in Aquem

Nestled in the heart of Aquem, **Shiva Family Restaurant** is making waves with an impressive **4.1 rating** from **843 reviews**. While this establishment may not be as widely touted as some of its competitors in Goa, it has garnered a loyal following, particularly for its standout menu featuring **fish thali** (18 mentions). Alongside this delightful dish, patrons frequently rave about the **prawns** (11 mentions), **curry** (11 mentions), and **rava fry** (10 mentions), making it a must-visit for seafood enthusiasts.

### Ambiance & Design

As you approach the restaurant, it presents a welcoming façade, easily accessible with street visibility—perfect for those exploring the area. Once inside, the ambiance strikes a balance between casual and comfortable. The decor is charming but understated, allowing the focus to shift towards the splendid meals served. Reviewers noted the good ambiance, though they remarked it wasn’t overwhelmingly spectacular. The ambient light offers a cozy glow, contributing to a relaxed dining experience. The friendly and cooperative staff adds warmth to the environment, making families feel right at home.

![Restaurant Interior](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlteNaSqzA5cMWWKO6JxZ8NAesU0Fuxd4-RvkCdnM3U7Zb2vKFdiRJyAzFKpe2nUNE2qxql4YTRo1ICRHWHoUJtG-i18RBOX6xjaVUjJQ2lwpTveGkZMo0BmTzYajWzsTk8h7eP=w750-h563-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The culinary journey at Shiva Family Restaurant is primarily centered around its seafood offerings, with the **fish thali** being hailed as "outstanding" by customers. This abundant platter showcases a variety of dishes, providing an authentic taste of Goan cuisine that is both affordable and flavorful. Reviewers appreciated the generous portions and the variety included in the thali. Other highlights include the **crispy chicken** and **cheese garlic naan**, which is described as an excellent combination, showcasing the restaurant's versatility.

The presentation of the dishes is simple yet inviting, capturing the essence of traditional home cooking. Many guests have mentioned that every dish was not just tasty but memorable, allowing them to relish the soulful tastes of Goan cooking.

### Customer Experience & Service

Shiva Family Restaurant shines in its customer service, as numerous reviews emphasize the friendliness and attentiveness of the staff. The efficiency of service is commendable, with patrons noting that placing orders and receiving meals is a smooth experience. Reservations are not required, making it a convenient option for families looking to enjoy a spontaneous meal together.

### Popularity & Reviews

While it might not be the most prominent name on the Goan culinary landscape, early diners at Shiva Family Restaurant are promoting it enthusiastically through glowing recommendations. Many have promised to return for the unforgettable fish thali alone, highlighting its standout status among similar establishments. The buzz on social media and the frequency of positive mentions hint at a growing reputation that is well-deserved.

### Utilizing Visual Content

The customer-provided images further enhance the experience of Shiva Family Restaurant. Photos reveal a clean, welcoming environment that feels immense yet intimate—a perfect place for families to gather. Each culinary plate shared on social platforms is visually appealing, showcasing the colorful and abundant nature of the fish thali, a calling card that beckons both locals and visitors alike. 

In conclusion, **Shiva Family Restaurant** offers a delightful dining experience centered around authentic Goan seafood, a welcoming atmosphere, and commendable service, making it a family-friendly spot worthy of exploration on your next trip to Aquem. With its notable fish thali taking center stage, it's no wonder this restaurant is quietly becoming a favorite among those in the know.
